summary: Just a RaceMenu preset of my character Saragahn.
descriptionHtml:
Won't be doing any updates for this, been having some issues with Skyrim and it's compatibility with Freckle Mania; will be releasing a new preset in it's stead when I'm able (I have to switch CBBE for UNP before I can release it).
For those unsure where the presets folder is: Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

Also Check out [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/66942/?]Esmerelda[/url], my second Preset.
